{"tid":1444193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國公安部：香港警察我們挺你！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:30:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53f92682ca1204dcfcd99cb08d8da0b68da5d285","tid":1444193,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"「守護香港大聯盟」昨日除前往多區警署向警員送上果籃和心意卡外，亦號召市民與警員合照，上載至facebook、微信朋友圈、Instagram等社交平台，並在帖文標籤「#全民撐警」、「#守護香港」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">央視、《人民日報》</span>等內地官媒亦有在微博上響應活動，紛紛表示「香港警察我們挺你」，相關帖文亦得到不少內地媒體或「大V」帳號轉發，如中國新聞網、內地的《經濟日報》、《揚子晚報》等。當中，央視的帖文更獲逾10萬人讚好。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">內地公安部</span>新聞中心微博「中國警方在線」亦有轉發帖文指，「今天，#全民撐警日# 一起轉發微博！告訴世界：中國早已不是1842年的中國。香港是中國的香港，不容外部勢力染指！#香港警察我們挺你#！」還配上了在內地網路走紅的「光頭劉Sir」漫畫。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2423995/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%97%A5%E3%80%8D%E7%8D%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%20%20%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%8C%BA%E4%BD%A0?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2423995%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2597%25A5%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%259F%25BF%25E6%2587%2589%2520%2520%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%258C%25BA%25E4%25BD%25A0%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=9bcfe3af\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2423995/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%97%A5%E3%80%8D%E7%8D%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%20%20%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%8C%BA%E4%BD%A0?mtc=10012</a><br />\n做到咁出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fb017449b3e8b334556521716c9ab6fd91f668","tid":1444193,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64d4e868d66e8346bf1b3281d542b3d57d10570","tid":1444193,"uid":2950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"香港是中國的香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9886e24ed26f38c9635688f54a538430a91df7","tid":1444193,"uid":259901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"梗係啦，公安睇到popo份糧已經流哂口水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cbe3b21130eb9a6a34335df8035098aad27015","tid":1444193,"uid":112581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:52:28.000Z","msg":"支那公安武警求其開槍打死人都唔洗負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dee097e442ee4e55ea15488b184f647529b56d6","tid":1444193,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64d4e868d66e8346bf1b3281d542b3d57d10570","tid":1444193,"uid":2950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"香港是中國的香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13e85cbcde7a3c7cba6e9ac6dd101abe4ed22c2","tid":1444193,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b89cbaea160b2677a862d9a10216a7bff142379","tid":1444193,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234fc23e13059407b7106af2f066b67c1ed98a03","tid":1444193,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"1842?共產黨出世未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c3b8c7b860e0e83ae838dd6bba25342bc7f96b","tid":1444193,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=d99c2a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">51,276</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 19:57）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"9dc482245c23614d82a5ccad8600f1774afee292","tid":1444193,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64d4e868d66e8346bf1b3281d542b3d57d10570","tid":1444193,"uid":2950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"香港是中國的香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"全宇宙都是中國的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MeBgj24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMeBgj24.png&h=af8ed99f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cad8f18ed1d40aa38f100c19fc9e93101420ca34","tid":1444193,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"重點係<br />\n1. 表態支持維穩（穩軍心）<br />\n2. 話示威者係外國勢力支持（淡化民主訴求）<br />\n3. 香港屬於中國（展示權力正當性、打飛機）<br />\n<br />\n=======================================<br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7AT6Db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7AT6Db.png&h=b6163964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a9140125cd2524e080af239b1e1c8065af2c47a","tid":1444193,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}